---
const GITHUB_URL = 'https://github.com/mymomot/gradatum';
const ARCH_URL = `${GITHUB_URL}/blob/main/ARCHITECTURE.md`;
---
<section class="hero section-pad" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow">Memoria · cognitive memory backbone for AI agents</div>

    <h1 id="hero-title" class="hero-h1">
      A place of<br />
      <em class="hero-accent">memory</em> for<br />
      your agents.
    </h1>

    <p class="hero-desc">
      Gradatum is a self-hosted, embedded memory backbone for multi-agent AI systems.
      It cures <em>memory rot</em> in LLMs and lets Claude, Gemini, Codex
      and your home-grown agents share what they know —
      across sessions, across machines, across runs.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-cta" role="group" aria-label="Primary actions">
      <a href={GITHUB_URL} class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Star on GitHub →
      </a>
      <a href={ARCH_URL} class="btn-text" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Read the architecture
      </a>
    </div>

    <blockquote class="cicero-quote" aria-label="Cicero, de Oratore II">
      <p>« Loci sunt, in quibus imagines collocantur. »</p>
      <footer>
        <span class="eyebrow">
          Cicero · de Oratore II — the loci are the places where images are set down.
        </span>
      </footer>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: var(--paper);
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero-h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 6.75rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
  }

  .hero-accent {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero-desc {
    margin-top: 2.25rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.4375rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 45rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .hero-desc em {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2.75rem;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 1rem 1.75rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
    min-height: 48px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .btn-text {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
    transition: color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    min-height: 48px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-text:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .cicero-quote {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1875rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 38rem;
  }

  .cicero-quote p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cicero-quote footer {
    font-style: normal;
    margin-top: 0.625rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
